{"tid":1201597,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《莎木3》PC 版確認於 Epic Game Store 獨家發售！！","createTime":"2019-06-11T05:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T12:05:07.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":88,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"711401868033f468a4e7e2efe9157d5465ade12a","tid":1201597,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:32:18.000Z","msg":"Ys Net 透過募資平台 Kickstarter 宣布，《莎木 3》PC 版本將會獨家在 Epic Games Store 發售<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，《莎木 3》使用 Epic Games 引擎開發，他們獲得 Epic 很多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，加上為了給予 PC 平台上最好的體驗，他們在與發行商 Deep Silver 多次討論後，決定 Epic Games Store 會是 PC 版最好的發行平台選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/5/180865.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F5%2F180865.html&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD6dOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=ffb64744\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/5/180865.html</a>"},{"pid":"cf72df2cff4d8284104eac1d448299764a518e11","tid":1201597,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:33:39.000Z","msg":"《莎木 3》是一手打造《莎木》系列的前 SEGA 遊戲創作者鈴木裕，單飛後創立 Ys Net 團隊透過群眾募資取得資金製作的系列最新作，將接續《莎木》、《莎木 2》未完結的故事。2015 年 E3 展透過 PlayStation 展前發表會首度公開。<br />\n<br />\n鈴木裕今日現身 PC Gaming Show 時表示，《莎木 3》遊戲開發工作已經接近尾聲。<br />\n<br />\nPC / PS4《莎木 3》今日同時宣布啟動預購，預定 11 月 19 日上市。"},{"pid":"85246a9209deba281afb9bf6604d5d597ea5dfed","tid":1201597,"uid":224565,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:35:37.000Z","msg":"epic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae8668d7e6cedbbef885cd8aede7bdc89fd7bde","tid":1201597,"uid":34409,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:35:53.000Z","msg":"之前眾籌果堆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2caf4da1fd1130c377015822e770f2a628e72e","tid":1201597,"uid":39628,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:37:28.000Z","msg":"有冇得退錢<br />\nEPIC一定唔裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e079f00c883d7dc39af707399192bcbd38b57d94","tid":1201597,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ae8668d7e6cedbbef885cd8aede7bdc89fd7bde","tid":1201597,"uid":34409,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:35:53.000Z","msg":"之前眾籌果堆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:38:23.000Z","msg":"買 ps4 版"},{"pid":"524a620f4495f73a0df201e2c8949f76af3284a0","tid":1201597,"uid":176303,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:39:00.000Z","msg":"EPIC?   OK 慳番筆"},{"pid":"92e5470fc30ae300ad7f304dea60c147c5845b34","tid":1201597,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"524a620f4495f73a0df201e2c8949f76af3284a0","tid":1201597,"uid":176303,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:39:00.000Z","msg":"EPIC?   OK 慳番筆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:39:22.000Z","msg":"買 ps4"},{"pid":"fe1a3ec9be7f982b0d18313813d514d23ca02012","tid":1201597,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:39:49.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"fccacbdf65113be6d7c44e2b5109469ada99881a","tid":1201597,"uid":34409,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e079f00c883d7dc39af707399192bcbd38b57d94","tid":1201597,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ae8668d7e6cedbbef885cd8aede7bdc89fd7bde","tid":1201597,"uid":34409,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:35:53.000Z","msg":"之前眾籌果堆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:38:23.000Z","msg":"買 ps4 版"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:44:54.000Z","msg":"有人話籌眾果時話係出steam版本"},{"pid":"05089c8e98faad31c37482bbe29be1edaddc6759","tid":1201597,"uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:46:24.000Z","msg":"【E3 2019】《莎木 3》PC版由 Epic Games Store獨占發售 玩家湧入募資平台要求退款<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gamebase.com.tw/news/topic/99198966/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamebase.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ftopic%2F99198966%2F&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD6dOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=fb479c08\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gamebase.com.tw/news/topic/99198966/</a><br />\n<br />\n鈴木裕領軍 Ys Net 團隊開發，Deep Sliver 發行 PS4 / PC 動作冒險遊戲《莎木 3》在 E3 期間舉辦的 The PC Gaming Show  上宣佈，PC 版將由 Epic Games Store  獨家發行，消息曝光後引起募資平台 Kickstarter 玩家極度不滿，紛紛要求退費。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.gbc.tw/gb_img/s300q80/3909993l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gbc.tw%2Fgb_img%2Fs300q80%2F3909993l.jpg&h=961e70f3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n由前 SEGA 遊戲《莎木》製作人鈴木裕宣佈啟動《莎木 3》開發計畫並且啟動募資專案，經由2015  E3 PlayStation 展前發表會公開消息的影響，獲得了 700 萬美元的募資金額，在 Kickstarter 上至少有69,320 位玩家響應募資。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.gbc.tw/gb_img/s300q80/3909994l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gbc.tw%2Fgb_img%2Fs300q80%2F3909994l.jpg&h=f27f1d3a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n日前宣佈《莎木 3》發行日期將從原訂的  8 月 27 日延期至 11 月 19 日之後，今日鈴木裕現身 The PC Gaming Show 帶來新宣傳影片，<span style=\"color: red;\">表示很榮幸成為 Epic Games Store 的獨佔遊戲</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，《莎木 3》在開發上使用 Unreal 引擎獲得 Epic 極大幫助，考量在 PC 上最好的體驗，與 Deep Sliver 共同決定將Epic Games Store 作為 PC 平台發售通路。考慮到使用 Unreal 引擎的遊戲在該平台有額外優惠抽成、以及發行商 Deep Sliver 先前也將《戰慄深邃：流亡》作為 EGS 獨占作品，此決定有跡可循。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.gbc.tw/gb_img/s300q80/3909995l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gbc.tw%2Fgb_img%2Fs300q80%2F3909995l.jpg&h=e5040979&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n消息一發表，在Kickstarter 的《莎木 3》募資專頁開始湧入憤怒的玩家，因為 Epic Games Store 成立以來的諸多負面消息包括獨佔商法、個人資料私隱疑雲等問題，參與募資的玩家要求 Ys Net 必須給予 Steam 版本的序號，否則要求退款的聲浪持續高漲中。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.gbc.tw/gb_img/s300q80/3909998l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gbc.tw%2Fgb_img%2Fs300q80%2F3909998l.jpg&h=144bee2e&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"cdca4f2d9aa90b4d6e46a725041da1cae3d89bd4","tid":1201597,"uid":91833,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:47:11.000Z","msg":"唔怪得俾中國 審批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc602c26f53b417536c2156f7aa17ef6f1897d06","tid":1201597,"uid":143231,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:29:16.000Z","msg":"冇得退款, 眾籌果班同香港市民一樣被人㩒住黎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb2b0f9cdcb4daf5f0349189814f4b419248b23","tid":1201597,"uid":140454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"等睇仆直了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20544052c7e23817cdd242431fde06516ce9854e","tid":1201597,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:32:56.000Z","msg":"有機會再延期。大陸做野有排攪"},{"pid":"10396308de050a10d4ca175888db57acb703aeab","tid":1201597,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40cf687e7eabd34b763f79a7499c1d9ec5540620","tid":1201597,"uid":19305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:34:40.000Z","msg":"已經fans向仲要倒自己米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos